Anova Analysis

In [65]:
import scipy.stats as stats
group1 = df_clean.absenteeism_time_in_hours
group2 = df_clean.age
group3 = df_clean.service_time

# Performing one-way ANOVA
f_statistic, p_value = stats.f_oneway(group1, group2, group3)

# Displaying results
print("ANOVA Statistic:", f_statistic)
print("P-value:", p_value)

# Interpretation
alpha = 0.05
if p_value < alpha:
    print("Reject the null hypothesis. There is a significant difference between the means.")
else:
    print("Fail to reject the null hypothesis. There is no significant difference between the means.")

ANOVA Statistic: 2283.4528652366844
P-value: 0.0
Reject the null hypothesis. There is a significant difference between the means.

CHI-SQUARE TEST

In [66]:
df_clean['disciplinary_failure'] = df_clean['disciplinary_failure'].astype(str)
df_clean['social_drinker'] = df_clean['social_drinker'].astype(str)
crosstab = pd.crosstab(df_clean["disciplinary_failure"], df_clean["absenteeism_time_in_hours"])

def probs(df_clean, child, parent1=None, parent2=None, parent3=None):
    if parent1==None:
        # Calculate probabilities
        prob=pd.crosstab(df_clean[child], 'Empty', margins=False, normalize='columns').sort_index().to_numpy().reshape(-1).tolist()
    elif parent1!=None:
            if parent2!=None:
                if parent3!=None:
                    # Caclucate probabilities
                    prob=pd.crosstab([df_clean[parent1],data[parent2], df_clean[parent3]],df_clean[child], margins=False, normalize='index').sort_index().to_numpy().reshape(-1).tolist()
                else:
                    # Caclucate probabilities
                    prob=pd.crosstab([df_clean[parent1],df_clean[parent2]],df_clean[child], margins=False, normalize='index').sort_index().to_numpy().reshape(-1).tolist()
            else:
                # Caclucate probabilities
                prob=pd.crosstab(df_clean[parent1],df_clean[child], margins=False, normalize='index').sort_index().to_numpy().reshape(-1).tolist()                
    else: print("Error in Probability Frequency Calculations")
    return prob

In [53]:
# Create nodes by using our earlier function to automatically calculate probabilities
social_drinker = BbnNode(Variable(0, 'social_drinker', ['Yes', 'No']), probs(df_clean, child='social_drinker'))
social_smoker = BbnNode(Variable(1, 'social_smoker', ['Yes', 'No']), probs(df_clean, child='social_smoker'))
disciplinary_failure = BbnNode(Variable(2, 'disciplinary_failure', ['Yes', 'No']), probs(df_clean, child='disciplinary_failure'))
education = BbnNode(Variable(3, 'education', ['Yes', 'No']), probs(df_clean, child='education', parent1='social_drinker', parent2='social_smoker'))
seasons = BbnNode(Variable(4, 'seasons', ['Summer', 'Autumn', 'Winter', 'Spring']), probs(df_clean, child='seasons',parent1='social_smoker',parent2='disciplinary_failure'))
absence_reason = BbnNode(Variable(5, 'absence_reason', ['No_absence', 'Medical', 'Not_Medical']), probs(df_clean, child='absence_reason', parent1='social_smoker',parent2='disciplinary_failure'))
distance_from_residence_to_work = BbnNode(Variable(6, 'distance_from_residence_to_work', ['Not_far', 'Near', 'Not_mention']), probs(df_clean, child='distance_from_residence_to_work',parent1='education',parent2='absence_reason'))
In [56]:
# join the BBN nodes into a network
# Create Network
bbn = Bbn() \
    .add_node(social_drinker) \
    .add_node(social_smoker) \
    .add_node(disciplinary_failure) \
    .add_node(education) \
    .add_node(seasons) \
    .add_node(absence_reason) \
    .add_node(distance_from_residence_to_work) \
    .add_edge(Edge(social_drinker,education, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(social_smoker, education, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(social_smoker, seasons, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge( seasons, social_drinker, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(disciplinary_failure, seasons, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(social_smoker, absence_reason,  EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(disciplinary_failure, absence_reason, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(education, distance_from_residence_to_work, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \
    .add_edge(Edge(absence_reason, distance_from_residence_to_work, EdgeType.DIRECTED)) \

print(bbn)
